World "LogicWorld"
Title "The World of Logic"

Introduction
"
We start out journey by introducing the elementary statement types.
For each type `T` we discuss two tactics. One of them allows us
to get a proof for `T` while the other enables us to use
information hidden in a hypothesis of type `T`.
